sub_title: Science Department Head, IB Math and Physics Teacher at Nord Anglia International School Rotterdam
summary:
I am an IB Math and Physics teacher, currently working at Nord Anglia International School Rotterdam. I have taught IB Math SL, IB Math HL, and IB Physics for the past six years at my current school.  

I am an effective and organized educator with ten plus years of experience of working with a wide variety of students. I am also experienced with variety of learning strategies to foster an engaging and student-centered learning enivronment.
